  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/6d6a15b538ffa2656d50ab4f2d324499.avif?t=1731534979\" width=617 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a distant future, mankind has landed on the asteroid X-474 to mine extremely rare minerals, but after many mysterious accidents the communications with the asteroid crew members has been lost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/e14bb9849f90cd3476c57d33c31ad488.poster.avif?t=1731534979\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/e14bb9849f90cd3476c57d33c31ad488.webm?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/e14bb9849f90cd3476c57d33c31ad488.mp4?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Luna, member of the investigation team sent to survey the activities on the asteroid, unfortunately you will find alien creatures has attacked the facilities and, you sole mission is to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/1883618c8a8353aede9382c067b035d0.poster.avif?t=1731534979\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/1883618c8a8353aede9382c067b035d0.webm?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/1883618c8a8353aede9382c067b035d0.mp4?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your weapons and destroy every enemy who tries to stop you in this amazing arcade style third person shooter game full of action, creatures and explosions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/34f33790340b5fa56c01e6e1a02e2850.poster.avif?t=1731534979\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/34f33790340b5fa56c01e6e1a02e2850.webm?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/34f33790340b5fa56c01e6e1a02e2850.mp4?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/1180b2f02ae29fcf031fad9de78f1dd1.avif?t=1731534979\" width=617 height=125 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/6d6a15b538ffa2656d50ab4f2d324499.avif?t=1731534979\" width=617 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a distant future, mankind has landed on the asteroid X-474 to mine extremely rare minerals, but after many mysterious accidents the communications with the asteroid crew members has been lost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/e14bb9849f90cd3476c57d33c31ad488.poster.avif?t=1731534979\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/e14bb9849f90cd3476c57d33c31ad488.webm?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/e14bb9849f90cd3476c57d33c31ad488.mp4?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Luna, member of the investigation team sent to survey the activities on the asteroid, unfortunately you will find alien creatures has attacked the facilities and, you sole mission is to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/1883618c8a8353aede9382c067b035d0.poster.avif?t=1731534979\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/1883618c8a8353aede9382c067b035d0.webm?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/1883618c8a8353aede9382c067b035d0.mp4?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your weapons and destroy every enemy who tries to stop you in this amazing arcade style third person shooter game full of action, creatures and explosions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/34f33790340b5fa56c01e6e1a02e2850.poster.avif?t=1731534979\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/34f33790340b5fa56c01e6e1a02e2850.webm?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/34f33790340b5fa56c01e6e1a02e2850.mp4?t=1731534979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545790/extras/1180b2f02ae29fcf031fad9de78f1dd1.avif?t=1731534979\" width=617 height=125 /></span></p>",
